title: Huge stack of VW mags - free - West Berks

posts.content:
[attachment=0]A70602C5-1713-4814-BD83-B87E287AEF0C.jpeg[/attachment][attachment=0]A70602C5-1713-4814-BD83-B87E287AEF0C.jpeg[/attachment]I’m trying to clear space. I’ve got a huge stack of VW mags from 2004 up to probably 2013. Probably 1.25m tall. There are lots of them.

Free to whoever wants to come and collect them, Please don’t ask me to post or search for a particular issue, I don’t have the time.
